# Egress allow-list for the secure-exec installer proxy (tinyproxy Filter file).
#
# With `FilterDefaultDeny Yes`, ONLY hosts matching a line here may be reached;
# everything else is refused. Patterns are extended regular expressions matched
# against the destination host (FilterExtended On). Anchored to avoid a
# substring like "pypi.org.evil.com" slipping through.
#
# pip talks to exactly two hosts:
#   - pypi.org                -> the package index / Simple API
#   - files.pythonhosted.org  -> the actual wheel/sdist downloads (Fastly CDN)
^pypi\.org$
^files\.pythonhosted\.org$